title: Snaps - Scott Frost to blame for Nebraska loss? Jim Harbaugh's crazy plan, chaos at Auburn
itunes:title: Snaps - Scott Frost to blame for Nebraska loss? Jim Harbaugh's crazy plan, chaos at Auburn
description:
T-Bob Hebert and Aaron Murray discuss Nebraska's shocking Week 0 loss to Northwestern and whether the blame should be placed on Scott Frost, Jim Harbaugh's plan for Michigan's quarterback situation, and Auburn athletic director Allen Greene stepping down from his role. #Herd
